ðŸš€ Summary
âœ… Enable SQL Server Authentication.
âœ… Grant lahari login permissions in SQL Server.
âœ… Enable TCP/IP in SQL Server Configuration Manager.
âœ… Allow Port 1433 in the Firewall.
âœ… Try connecting with 127.0.0.1,1433 instead of HELLO\SQLEXPRESS.
